                  Haizhen Qi and
                  Gang Yang and
                  Jin'ao Cuil and
                  Gen Li and
                  Yue Song},
	title = {DoS-Dam: a Hierarchical Method for Identifying and Mitigating DDoS
                  Attacks in High-Speed Network Traffic},
	booktitle = {32nd {IEEE} International Conference on Network Protocols, {ICNP}
                  2024, Charleroi, Belgium, October 28-31, 2024},
